title: Anarchy in Manchester 1977 So It Goes New Wave ITV Doc.
description:
Various Artists
Anarchy In Manchester
"So It Goes"
A New Wave music series originally broadcast by ITV (Granada TV)-1977
Repackaged into 6 episodes and Rebroadcast by SKY ARTS 1 October-November 2014 (ads removed)
